{"tid":801753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【珠光寶氣】陳思齊息影做骨妹　當年整完容個樣真係嚇親人","createTime":"2018-09-01T02:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T10:53:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f47fa73ff5ee3c7177deee196f3b8422a63ee6ca","tid":801753,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1809902/org/0c9dcbccbd67bc9230d1cd618d5735f6.jpg/RjQqXCQpBSLx7hopmdoH4QURq50QO1q5XWytS11srUs?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1809902%2Forg%2F0c9dcbccbd67bc9230d1cd618d5735f6.jpg%2FRjQqXCQpBSLx7hopmdoH4QURq50QO1q5XWytS11srUs%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=462a753b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1810166/org/a1e5bbcfa61a717fa573f9531d6a66cd.jpg/3Nw1MY-cHlNpN0ZYb1yPY6vldLy1LL3YTqI3kE6iN5A?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1810166%2Forg%2Fa1e5bbcfa61a717fa573f9531d6a66cd.jpg%2F3Nw1MY-cHlNpN0ZYb1yPY6vldLy1LL3YTqI3kE6iN5A%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=df2b87f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1810169/org/7786544bf9e00b09bc8af78a671e8500.jpg/ETI8tqacMCM6J_q19pQGUal-qCndR8hftaRM9rWkTPY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1810169%2Forg%2F7786544bf9e00b09bc8af78a671e8500.jpg%2FETI8tqacMCM6J_q19pQGUal-qCndR8hftaRM9rWkTPY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b43a5acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《珠光寶氣》晚晚播，每次都有一些舊面孔重新映入觀眾的眼簾，在昨晚的那集，為關禮傑報紙檔執頭執尾的女生，就是飾演他女友關靜的陳思齊（原名陳凱怡），原來她已經退出了娛樂圈，還轉行做骨妹。<br />\n<br />\n陳思齊於2000年參選港姐入行，同屆參賽的還有簡慕華、岑寶兒等人，「大小姐」林淑敏等人賽前被傳媒喻為「翻版朱玲玲」而成為大熱的她卻三甲不進，有人說是因為當初她的一句「朱玲玲係邊個？」得罪人，所以最終無獎落袋。<br />\n<br />\n雖然落選，但依然被TVB睇中簽為藝人，從而開展她的演藝生涯，在TVB的12年間拍過上百部劇集，但只有少數令人印象深刻，包括《老婆大人》中的Bobo和《碧血鹽梟》中的四小姐。在2013年離開TVB去港視發展，本來都備受重用，可惜因為牌照事件令港視無以為繼，而陳思齊則退出了娛樂圈，轉行做骨妹。<br />\n<br />\n這裡說的骨妹，在她早前接受其他傳媒訪問時表示，是用香薰按摩幫客人減壓舒緩，而且她只接女客人，更為這份工作進修了音樂治療及香薰按摩和的課程。陳思齊指自己去學的原因，是因為媽媽老紀大有「五十肩」，孝順女的她當然想給媽媽最好的服務，而這件事更成為了自身的工作，一舉兩得。<br />\n<br />\n雖然演藝事業未算出位，不過當年有單新聞就令人相當關注。話說在2013年的時候，她被傳出整容，原來她當時是因為去了做美容院的代言人，打了兩次透明質酸針，結果令到臉部浮腫。那時候有同事問她為什麼變了樣，她也直接答自己去了整容，不過之後她已經還原了整個臉容，到現在36歲依然是保持靚樣，其實本身咁靚又使乜整容呢！"},{"pid":"f75ee600890b4b5f869faabf9056e69c706181f7","tid":801753,"uid":99700,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1810169/org/7786544bf9e00b09bc8af78a671e8500.jpg/ETI8tqacMCM6J_q19pQGUal-qCndR8hftaRM9rWkTPY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1810169%2Forg%2F7786544bf9e00b09bc8af78a671e8500.jpg%2FETI8tqacMCM6J_q19pQGUal-qCndR8hftaRM9rWkTPY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b43a5acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee8aea4cf5010e8ad92a1a9406c88447aae56bd","tid":801753,"uid":62114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5d6cd2533444f543630cbcb8c89a2d7a35aae6","tid":801753,"uid":25635,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"我有段時間覺得佢同文頌嫻好似"},{"pid":"0e4f4f77d47cdbcf5d233259971a43830ea1eb3a","tid":801753,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"當年話打左botox<br />\n=透明質酸? 係會自體吸收?"},{"pid":"17da6dce4ef731161a1386f99f3ed465b68eacab","tid":801753,"uid":38049,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"骨妹..... 寫到人做雞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07117a03da22de65d4e7ea1e321c73d4000a3e3f","tid":801753,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"17da6dce4ef731161a1386f99f3ed465b68eacab","tid":801753,"uid":38049,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:00:1